{
  "stem": "2097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940, in September, the Hungarian, when they came-- oh, in 1939, because of this crowding situation what was in the city, the army and the-- somehow, the typhus broke out in Simleu.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father got the typhus, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taken to the hospital in Oradea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was staying with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in early, in about in July, 1930-- 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was very little-- one year and a--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--few months.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- we were taken by my mother, to my grandmother in Marghita.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was staying there with--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Simleu?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Marghita from Simleu is-- Marghita from Simleu is 20 kilometer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her mother-- my mother's mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's mother perished much before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the reason I have her name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother didn't want-- got very sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't want to be with nobody-- only with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in September, in 1940, when the Hungarian came with their army to occupy the part of Romania, I was actually a little bit further than-- we-- I went to the road where my grandmother lived.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw the Hungarian army coming in, with big parade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Oradea they were telling that only 6% of the army is Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The others, they were just Hungarians-- Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Hungary already was Jew law-- against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only 6% of the army was Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- but, you know, I was just-- at the time, I was 11.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In 1940, I was 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I saw the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were throwing flowers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And even the Jews, they were very happy, especially who served in-- in first world war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were decorated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they thought that they are getting-- that God is coming to the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
